    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a profile that is a superset of the connection to IPv6 cellular networks defined in the IPv6 for Third Generation Partnership Project (3GPP) Cellular Hosts document. This document defines a profile that is a superset of the connections to IPv6 cellular networks defined in "IPv6 for Third Generation Partnership Project (3GPP) Cellular Hosts" (RFC 7066).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Both mobile hosts and mobile devices with the capability to share their 3GPP mobile connectivity are in scope.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
